1.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隻蝗蟲未去過就唔好亂講啦<br />\n同廣州深圳一樣？<br />\n有街燈有馬路就叫一樣呀？<br />\n屌你啦！廣州啲路又殘又舊又污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最出名果條上下九路兩邊啲喇叭嘈到好似落disco咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳仲好笑，除左地王、乜春100大廈附近啲路叫做新少少之外，其他地方咪同東門一樣又殘又舊又污糟又臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣叫做同香港一樣？你搵旺角條後巷比呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n </span>"},{"pid":"780b759998696e8413543202f5b82881b40cdc98","tid":649132,"uid":99856,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁你又黎? 呢D新聞一年冇十單都八單,屌喇星"},{"pid":"d7cf184f8726b3138caeff8d5d4cdbf88c81bf4e","tid":649132,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c76dd5f4e7b7a0e42294107afa418c6d08698b9","tid":649132,"uid":27451,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ac65c4355307ab2522b76d6200af7bd0bc6b2c7d","tid":649132,"uid":35014,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"其實香港都好多淘實野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"最斃佢買啲藥唔係淘寶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86869a4247b8bbf5fefc574c891bdd749e45af1","tid":649132,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T10:04:48.000Z","msg":"]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛未來撚啊廢扮泛民打手<br />\n實質同其他五毛一唱一和<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122237_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.ne